text: Barantsevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Kaltymanovsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 85 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 24 km from Iglino, 6 km from Kaltymanovo. == See also == *Barantsev == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Barantsevo
